{"fadein":1.5,"once":true,"id":"TIERBICI7","fadeType":2,"mode":2,"fadeOut":1.5,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"sequence":[["「Schmelzen」\n\n<size=45>Chapter 7: Warmth<\/size>",1]],"stopbgm":true},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"After that, some time passed...","blackBg":true,"dir":1},{"bgName":"bg_night","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"blackBg":true,"flashin":{"black":true,"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0]},"side":2,"bgm":"story-2","say":"Port - Outskirts","dir":1,"bgmDelay":2,"flashout":{"black":true,"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1]}},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_night","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Tirpitz invited me to come talk to her, and I ended up somewhere up high at the outskirts of the port.","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_night","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Sorry for having you come out to a place like this.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":405020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_night","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"The truth is, there's something I wanted to see with you.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":405020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_night","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Tirpitz pointed at something shimmering in the sky.","dir":1,"options":[{"flag":1,"content":"The North Star?"}]},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_night","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Yes, the Polarstern.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":405020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_night","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Whenever I look at this star, I'm reminded of my past... that time I was locked down in port, a \"fleet in name only.\"","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":405020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_night","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I spent day after day doing nothing, feeling nothing, just simply used to being cold and alone.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":405020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_night","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"And then, having achieved nothing of note, I met my end, watching the smoke of despair fill the harbor as I welcomed my destruction.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":405020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_night","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Don't you agree that I had a ridiculous, empty life?","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":405020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_night","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":405020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_night","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"But now, things are different.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":405020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_night","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Now there is the joy of meeting people, and the peace of mind from being with you. And the warmth of it was able to melt away the ice of my past.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":405020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_night","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"\"The Lone Queen of the North\" is alone no longer.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":405020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_night","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I pray that the other me in the mirror - and in my dreams - will be as happy as the me here right now...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":405020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_night","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"... I think I'm a little tired.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":405020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_night","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"I feel the weight of her resting against my shoulder.","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_night","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Say, would you mind if I pull up closer to you...?","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":405020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_night","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I want to feel your warmth for a little bit longer...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":405020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_night","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Tirpitz's warm voice, almost in a whisper, filled your ears.","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_night","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"I hope she stays this gentle, now and forever.","blackBg":true,"dir":1}]}